WEBVTT

00:02.101 --> 00:04.536
- [panting]
what is that?

00:04.538 --> 00:05.837
- That's my new
runner's watch.

00:05.839 --> 00:08.874
It's got everything--
tracks how far you've run,

00:08.876 --> 00:10.142
Your heart rate,
calories burned.

00:10.144 --> 00:13.645
It's got gps to tell you
exactly where you are.

00:13.647 --> 00:14.913
And if I ever lose it,

00:14.915 --> 00:18.183
I can pinpoint exactly
where it is on my cell phone.

00:18.185 --> 00:19.418
Huh?

00:19.420 --> 00:21.920
- [panting]

00:21.922 --> 00:23.688
How far have we gone?

00:23.690 --> 00:25.857
- Uh, 0.04 miles.

00:25.859 --> 00:28.794
- What? We've been
jogging forever.

00:28.796 --> 00:31.930
- We've been jogging
for 20 seconds.

00:31.932 --> 00:34.599
- Does that thing have
a defibrillator?

00:34.601 --> 00:35.667
- No. Why?

00:35.669 --> 00:38.503
- Because I think
my heart just stopped.

00:38.505 --> 00:40.972
No, wait.

00:40.974 --> 00:43.708
There it is.

00:43.710 --> 00:46.778
I think I'm gonna
head home.

00:46.780 --> 00:49.848
No way.
That is too far.

00:49.850 --> 00:51.450
I'd never make it.

00:51.452 --> 00:55.020
Maybe I'll just wait here
till bugs gets back.

00:55.022 --> 00:57.055
He can carry me.

00:57.057 --> 00:58.890
Uhh!

